title: Q1-TECH, 1Pcs White Hide Away Strobe Tubes Replacement Bulbs for 80W / 120W / 160W Hide A Way HID Emergency Hazard Warning Headlight Strobe Light Kit System (Blue)
features: FEATURES: 1Pcs HID Strobe Lights Bulbs, Super-Bright, white light. Universal for all vehicles with 12V-24V power source supply. Bulbs have a rubber grommet base, designed to easily install into a 1 inch hole, which is drilled into each headlight, front side marker and taillight assembly.
Waterproof Shell and Universal - This light bar part is weather proof, it can be used under any conditions; This Strobe Light Bar fits for all vehicle with a 12V power source.
Fitment: Bulbs may be installed into any 1 inch diameter hole in corner lights, headlights, tail lights, etc ( if no hole exists drilling may be required ) Can be seen during daylight

HID Strobe Light Bulb SPECIFICATIONS:: Bulbs 1 3/4 inch height 1 inch Bottom 1 1/2 inch Base. Designed for reliability and high performance, are encapsulated in silicon for moisture protection and to protect against road vibration.

Note#: It is a universal replacement bulb tube for HID HIDE A WAY system. However, if you purchased the HID Bulbs Hide-a-way kit through other channels and installed it to cause the HID HIDE A WAY system to malfunction, we are not responsible for compatibility or ' DO NOT MATCH '.
PACKAGE INCLUDES:: 1 x HID Strobe Light Bulb
